# Re-assert the Pangolin firewall allowance in case Tailscale re-inserts its
# ts-input jump above our ACCEPT rule after a restart. This is a cheap check:
# in steady state it is a single read-only "iptables -S INPUT" per address
# family and changes nothing unless our rule has fallen below ts-input.
*/1 * * * * /etc/rc.d/rc.pangolin fw-heal &> /dev/null
